{"name": "villog", "metadata": {"name": "villog", "version": "0.1.7", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["xlsxwriter"], "summary": "A simple python utility tool for your everyday projects.", "upload_time": 1735899249}, "documentation": ["# Villog is a simple python utility tool for your everyday projects.\n\n## Logger\n```\nfrom villog import Logger\n\nl: Logger = Logger(\n    file_path = \"test.log\",\n    encoding = \"utf-8-sig\",\n    time_format = \"%Y.%m.%d %H:%M:%S\",\n    separator = \"\\t\",\n    silent = False,\n    enable_remove = False,\n    strip_content = False\n)\n\nl.log(\n    content = \"test\"\n)\n```\n\n## Writexcel\n```\nfrom villog.writexcel import WorkSheet, WorkBook\n\nsheet_1: WorkSheet = WorkSheet(\n    name = \"Sheet1\",\n    header = [\"header_1\", \"header_2\", \"header_3\"],\n    data = [\n        [\"data_1\", \"data_2\", \"data_3\"],\n        [\"data_4\", \"data_5\", \"data_6\"]\n    ]\n)\n\nsheet_2: WorkSheet = WorkSheet(\n    name = \"Sheet2\",\n    header = [\"header_1\", \"header_2\", \"header_3\"],\n    data = [\n        [\"data_1\", \"data_2\", \"data_3\"],\n        [\"data_4\", \"data_5\", \"data_6\"]\n    ]\n)\n\nbook: WorkBook = WorkBook(\n    name = \"Book1\",\n    sheets = [sheet_1, sheet_2]\n)\n\nbook.xlsx_create(\n    file_path = \"test.xlsx\"\n)\n```\n\n## Install\nWith **pip**:\n```\npip install villog\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "villog.utils", "documentation": ["utility functions"], "functions": [{"name": "villog.utils.gen_uuid", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "length", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Generating a random UUID\n\nParameters:\n    length (int): length of the UUID"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"nam